      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light leading-tight mb-6">Dental Implant Insurance Coverage</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 leading-8 text-lg max-w-3xl">Dental implant coverage varies widely. Some plans help with parts of treatment, some exclude implants, and many plans are limited by annual maximums.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
